title: Kendall Jenner & Gigi Hadid Grab Lunch After Olivier Rousteing's Birthday Party
text: Kendall Jenner leads the way after grabbing lunch with gal pals Gigi Hadid and Cara Delevingne in Los Angeles on Saturday afternoon (October 24). Just the night before, the three models joined Kendall‘s younger sister, Kylie, at Olivier Rousteing‘s birthday party.
